uniol.apt.analysis.cycles.lts

Class ComputeSmallestCycles

  • java.lang.Object
    • uniol.apt.analysis.cycles.lts.ComputeSmallestCycles

  • public class ComputeSmallestCycles
extends java.lang.Object
    This class computes smallest cycles and parikh vectors, checking if all smallest cycles having the same parikh vector, or having the same or mutually disjoint parikh vectors.
    Author:
    Chris, Manuel
